data.description: Spacious brick home located in established neighborhood in Dothan that is convenient to everything. Inside you will find 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, 2 separate living areas, formal dining room and an eat in kitchen with a large bar area. The inside laundry room has ample storage and is right off the garage. Outside is an inviting open patio for grilling and relaxing by the pool.  The back yard has a privacy fence surrounding the pool as well as a storage shed for tools and an extra paved area for a basketball set up or lawn equipment.
